-- GM CEO Wagoner to step down: report
-- 
-- Sun Mar 29, 2009 5:02pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/29/us-generalmotors-idUSTRE52S1YN20090329

 

 (Reuters) - General Motors Corp CEO Rick Wagoner is going to step down, Bloomberg reported on Sunday. 

 Bloomberg says people familiar with situation did not say why Wagoner is leaving.